caption.p: Three-dimensional ( right) and two-dimensional ( left) closest interactions between active site residues of peroxiredoxin 5 and some molecules belonging to different class compounds with the best score result. Legend: ( A): Compound 13 (CMP-N-acetylneuraminic acid, Class: Amino Sugar), ( B): Compound 14 (Carapin-8 (9)-Ene, Class: Limnoid), ( C): Compound 10 (Sericetin diacetate, Class: Flavonol), and ( D): Compound 8 (Cepharantine, Class: Alkaloid).
